<plot>A Tale of Bad Luck is an animated story in the wondrous style of the silent film era. Set in a surreal toy landscape, Ted, a toy bear is separated by fate from Dolly, the toy that he loves. Bad luck continues to plague him in his undaunted quest to reunite with his one true love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016847</url></doc>
